Setting.py : Secrete_key

-pip install python-decouple
-settings.py: from decouple import config
- SECRET_KEY= config('SECRET_KEY')
- create .env file in root directory 
		write here: SECRETE_KEY=
- pip install django-extensions
-add installed app in setting.py: 'django_extensions'
-run: python manage.py generate_secret_key
 secret_key will be generated: copy it and paset it in .env file
- keep this env file into .ignore file

In production:
	p-pip install python-decouple
-settings.py: from decouple import config
- SECRET_KEY= config('SECRET_KEY')
-pip install django-extensions

add the SECRET_KEY in environmentvariable as variable:
	Name:SECRET_KEY
	Value:SECRET_KEY